# No environment variables needed.
# The waitlist is handled by Tally (tally.so) — a free hosted form service.
#
# To set up:
# 1. Create a free account at https://tally.so
# 2. Create a form with a single "Email" field
# 3. In Workspace settings → Notifications, add your email to get notified on each signup
# 4. Copy your form ID from the form URL (e.g. tally.so/r/FORMID)
# 5. Paste it into src/pages/index.astro where it says REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_TALLY_FORM_ID
